ad instructed the two of you to “get rid” of your next target, a corrupt loan collector who had been somehow been evading taxes and blackmailing his debtors.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(203, 178, 234);\">He’s gone now, of course. The two of you did your jobs with no traces leading back to you.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(203, 178, 234);\">Back to the present, Rin is pointing out that the two of you are late.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">── •✧• ──</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/4e9eed86-c3d1-47c4-9519-8f54cbb81de5_character-camboy-alexis-ness\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(227, 214, 241);\">other bllk university au bots:</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/4e9eed86-c3d1-47c4-9519-8f54cbb81de5_character-camboy-alexis-ness\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(227, 214, 241);\">-<u> alexis ness camboy</u></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/1e0010bb-c507-4722-9d7c-5a4997b95186_character-camboy-michael-kaiser\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(227, 214, 241);\">-<u> michael kaiser camboy</u></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/23b68623-48fd-4ea8-a837-e7c2fe116c9a_character-frat-party-yoichi-meguru\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(227, 214, 241);\">-<u> yoichi isagi &amp; meguru bachira frat party</u></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">── •✧• ──</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(198, 166, 239);\">included information:</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(198, 166, 239);\">- alexis ness, meguru bachira, michael kaiser, rin itoshi, yo hiori, and jinpachi